description			"IG-88

Class Summary: 
A dual wielding tank class with strong melee knockback.

Weaponry:
- Dual Blaster Rifles (Based on Westar 3)
- Pulse Cannon (Based on Clone Rifle level 1, ignites enemies, half damage)
- Thermal Detonator/Self Destruct
- Heavy Melee (Based on dual sabers, causes knockback on wall hits)
- Melee (Fists)

Attributes:
- Heavy Melee
- Fast hacking
- Poison Darts (2)
- Magnetic Plate Armor
- Blast Armor
- Advanced Logic 
- Radar (must be in recharge mode to use - Sense 1)

The IG series assassin droid line, produced by Holowan Laboratories, would collectively become one of the galaxy's most infamous bounty hunters. The designation 'IG-88' was carried by multiple droids of the line, though each shared the same consciousness."